<h2>LittleSis API v1.0</h2>

<p>The LittleSis API exposes the raw data used on the <?php echo link_to('LittleSis', 'http://littlesis.org') ?> website. The data consists of basic information about people and organizations ("entities"), and the relationships between them, and is licensed under a <a rel="license" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/us/">Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 United States License</a>. All information on LittleSis is entered by individual users or automatic scripts, and is based on reliable online sources such as newspapers, organization websites, and government agencies.<p>

<p>To use the LittleSis API, you must <?php echo link_to('register', '@register') ?> for an API key.</p>

<p>Please read the <?php echo link_to('documentation', '@documentation') ?> carefully before using this service.</p>